BACKGROUND.name = "Corporate Agent"
BACKGROUND.description = "Cut-throat business practices have always been your specialty. You’ve been climbing your way up the ladder for as long as you can remember, using whatever means you thought necessary to get there. The corporate world is unforgiving, and oftentimes cruel. But you’ve managed to navigate it well enough for it to feel like home.\n\nWhat mattered to you were results. While your practices have been called into question by your competition, your superiors, and your underlings, only you know that truth. Whether it was illegal operations, corporate dealings under the table, or legitimate business, it all served to progress your career on your way to the top.\n\nAs a member of the corporate sphere, you learned not just how to blend in, but how to impress your peers as well. You fit in among others in the private sector, and have a special way of influencing them."
